\par\pard\plain \fi360\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0 15. So Hagar bore Abram a son.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Contrast this with 16:1, which notes that Sarah has borne Abraham no children. The cost of Sarah\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s human engineering is to watch Hagar give birth to and raise a child for Abraham. The tension for the promised son is only heightened.}
